    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine domini nostri Iesu Christi Dei aeterni. <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/21">Berengarius</persName>
                        <rs key="#Emperor/king">rex</rs>. Si sacris locis et divinis cultibus
                        mancipatis emolumentum regalis celsitudinis exibemus, profuturum nobis hoc
                        ad aeterne remunerationis proemium facilius optinendum et ad presentem vitam
                        felicius transigendam fore nullatenus dubitamus. Quapropter omnium fidelium
                        sanctae Dei Aecclesiae nostrorumque presentium scilicet ac futurorum nosse
                        cupimus universitatis industriam, eo quod <rs key="#Intercessory">interventu
                            et petitione</rs>
                        <persName key="#Intercessory #Consiliarius_regis #Bishops" ref="#people/123"
                            >Adelardi</persName> venerabilis <rs key="#Bishops">episcopi</rs>
                        dilecti ac summi <rs key="#Consiliarius_regis">consiliarii</rs> nostri sacri
                        palatii <orgName key="#Curtes #Fundi #Mansi" ref="#juridical_persons/30"><rs
                                key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs> Novo</orgName> quandam <rs
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >mansiculam</rs> cum <rs
                            key="#Fundi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >orticello</rs> pertinentem de <rs
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >curte</rs> rei publicae nostrae <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fundi #Mansi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/91">Muciana</geogName> civitate <placeName ref="#places/9"
                            >Brixia</placeName> concedimus, quam ex omni parte res eiusdem
                        monasterii circumdant, solumodo a meridie <rs key="#Roads">via publica</rs>,
                        quam <rs
                            key="#Curtes #Fundi #Mansi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >de nostro iure et potestate in eius ius et potestate</rs> modis omnibus
                        transfundimus et perdonamus, ut habeat, teneat, atque possideat <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure">iure
                            perpetuo ac pacifico</rs>. Si quis autem contra hoc nostrae donationis
                        preceptum quandoque insurgere temtaverit, sciat se compositurum <rs
                            key="#Penalty">mille mancosos aureos</rs>, <rs key="#Camera_regis"
                            >medietatem palatio nostro</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Camera_of_other_public_authorities">medietatem sepe nominato
                            monasterio</rs>. Ut autem ab omnibus verius credatur diligentiusque
                        observetur, manu propria subter confirmavimus et anuli nostri inpressione
                        insigniri iussimus. Signum domni Berengarii gloriosissimi regis. <persName
                            key="#Notary"><name ref="Liutwardus">Liutardus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> ad vicem <persName
                            key="#Archchancellor #Bishops" ref="#people/123">Adelardi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopi</rs> et <rs key="#Archchancellor"
                            >archicancellarii</rs> recognovi et subscripsi. Data kal. Septemb., anno
                        incarnationis Domini DCCCLXXXVIIII anno vero regni domno Berengarii II,
                        indictione VII. Actum <placeName ref="#places/58">Cremona</placeName>. In
                        Dei nomine feliciter, amen.</ab>
